name: Dogu Spectre
description:
#05/07 of DOGU - White Series

Dogu Spectre is a mischievous being. It can materialize only for a moment and uses the short time it has in a material world to wreak havoc. And what kind of havoc would it be? Dogu Spectre moves all the socks it can find slightly to the left and then disappears to the netherworld. The horror!

---

The White Series focuses on combining old nature pictures with the DOGUs.

This series consists of 6 DOGUs and one secret DOGU.
